title: Heys Luggage - Ambitus Apex Luggage
description: Established in 1986, in the suburbs of Toronto, Heys® International Ltd. has since become a global leader in luggage design and is synonymous with luxurious, fashionable lightweight luggage with high standard for excellence in workmanship and quality.
transcripts:
Heys Luggage is proud to offer a choice of the Ambitus or the Apex. Both are three-piece, lightweight spinner luggage sets made from a polycarbonate composite material. The Ambitus comes with a unique, attractive pattern on the outer shell, while the Apex has a more traditional, yet stylish, look. Both are made from polycarbonate composite, the same material used in the making of bulletproof glass. 

They have stylish, color-matching accents on their exteriors, and a specially designed, diamond-embossed texture. This surface texture reduces scratches and marks from forming on the shell. It adds to the durability of the luggage, and keeps it looking great trip after trip. 

Its frameless design removes the need for traditional luggage frames, thereby making it incredibly lightweight. Their spinner wheels are adaptable. They can be used to roll the luggage behind you in the traditional two-wheel , method, or you can use all four wheels and roll it alongside you. These spinner wheels have you covered for whatever terrain you may encounter. Not only are they tough and durable, but they are also incredibly easy to spin. 

The interior is fully lined with a stylish pattern. It comes with a see-through zipper divider that allows for organized packing and easy access to the underside. It also has a unique packing strap that includes a handy zippered mesh pocket for extra storage. Both styles have a zipper-released expansion system, which allows up to 20% more packing space. 

The Heys Ambitus and Apex offer a great choice. They are richly featured, and made from a durable, polycarbonate composite material, all the while being incredibly lightweight. The Ambitus and Apex spinners by Heys.
